    LoseCardEvents:
    - EventID: People_Downfull
      EventImageID: CityInFire
      CharacterID: Dead
      Title: Rebellion
      Text: Crowds fill the streets, anger and discontent tear apart the old order.
        The emperor no longer controls the plebs; chaos engulfs Rome.
      LeftText: Accept Doom
      RightText: Accept Doom
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: People_Overfull
      EventImageID: Popular
      CharacterID: Lose
      Title: Populists Replace the Emperor
      Text: "Under the pressure of the crowd, the old orders collapse, the plebs
        shape Rome\u2019s fate, and the emperor\u2019s power vanishes."
      LeftText: Accept Defeat
      RightText: Accept Defeat
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: Army_Downfull
      EventImageID: Legion
      CharacterID: Lose
      Title: Empire Collapsed
      Text: Legions have scattered across the provinces; there is no longer strength
        to hold the borders, and enemies are already raising armies against Rome.
      LeftText: Accept Defeat
      RightText: Accept Defeat
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: Army_Overfull
      EventImageID: Legion
      CharacterID: Dead
      Title: Military Coup
      Text: Generals have amassed too much power and stage a revolt. The iron discipline
        of the legions has become a threat to the emperor himself.
      LeftText: Accept Doom
      RightText: Accept Doom
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: Gold_Downfull
      EventImageID: Street
      CharacterID: Dead
      Title: Merchants Seize Power
      Text: "The treasury is empty\u2014no one wishes to obey anymore. Merchants
        take control, and the empire loses influence and resources, betraying the
        emperor."
      LeftText: Accept Doom
      RightText: Accept Doom
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: Gold_Overfull
      EventImageID: Inside
      CharacterID: Dead
      Title: "Emperor\u2019s Greed"
      Text: "The treasury is full\u2014you are accused of greed and overthrown in
        favor of another ruler. The people and senators lose trust; the treasury
        becomes a source of intrigue and downfall."
      LeftText: Accept Doom
      RightText: Accept Doom
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: Senate_Downfull
      EventImageID: Inside
      CharacterID: Dead
      Title: Senate Against the Emperor
      Text: The Senate declares the emperor an enemy of the republic. Aristocrats
        rebel, laws are not passed, and the emperor loses support in the halls of
        powe
      LeftText: Accept Doom
      RightText: Accept Doom
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
    - EventID: Senate_Overfull
      EventImageID: Inside
      CharacterID: Lose
      Title: Senate Turns Puppet
      Text: "The Senate limits the emperor\u2019s power and turns him into a puppet.
        Aristocrats rule the country behind the ruler\u2019s back, and Rome loses
        real central authority."
      LeftText: Accept Defeat
      RightText: Accept Defeat
      LeftResources: 
      RightResources: 
      NextLeft: GameOver
      NextRight: GameOver
      Weight: 0
      Condition: 
      onlyChoiceThisCard: 0
      WaitToPlay: 0
